TOP 20 JOB ROLES IN BLOCKCHAIN
(With Roles, Required Skills & Final Job Skills Summary)

1. Blockchain Developer
Role:
Develops blockchain platforms and solutions
Required Skills:
Python, Java, C++
Blockchain fundamentals
Cryptography
Ethereum / Hyperledger

2. Smart Contract Developer
Role:
Writes and deploys smart contracts
Required Skills:
Solidity / Vyper
Ethereum, Remix
Web3.js / Ethers.js
Smart contract security

3. Blockchain Architect
Role:
Designs blockchain system architecture
Required Skills:
System design
Consensus mechanisms
Security architecture
Cloud platforms

4. Blockchain Engineer
Role:
