üîë JOB SKILLS SUMMARY (BLOCKCHAIN CAREERS)
Blockchain careers require a combination of technical, analytical, and soft skills
Core blockchain fundamentals are essential for all roles
Programming skills are required for developer and engineering positions
Smart contract expertise is crucial for Ethereum, DeFi, and NFT roles
Security and cryptography knowledge ensures system and asset protection
Data analysis and financial understanding support analyst and research roles
UI/UX and frontend skills enhance Web3 usability
Legal and regulatory awareness is important for compliance and consulting roles
Communication and teamwork skills are required across all blockchain jobs
Continuous learning is essential due to the rapid evolution of blockchain technology

üìù   Summary:
Blockchain careers demand strong blockchain fundamentals, programming and smart contract skills, security awareness, analytical thinking, and effective communication skills.

